headline: Nvidia, Macy’s, Walmart: 3 shocking PE ratios investors need to know
summary: Yahoo Finance Executive Editor Brian Sozzi on Morning Brief to take a look at three forward price-to-earnings (P/E) ratios that he's watching: Macy's (M), Walmart (WMT), and Nvidia (NVDA). Market Domination Julie Hyman also discusses the high forward P/E ratios of Tesla (TSLA) and Palantir (PLTR). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Morning Brief here. This post was written by Naomi Buchanan.

headline: Palantir Needs An Nvidia Moment To Justify Its Valuation
summary: Palantir's 30% YoY revenue increase raises questions on valuation. See why PLTR stock may need Nvidia-like growth to justify current levels.
